{"tid":712363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海毛蟲原","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:13:10.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9a1c62eada997d56f1c38f0b757783b4be4aac","tid":712363,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/海毛蟲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%B5%B7%E6%AF%9B%E8%9F%B2&d=%2BRw2xM0Hd4f155oiEcL3QxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9e98b23d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/海毛蟲</a><br />\n<br />\n海毛蟲（英語：ciliate，學名：Ciliophora），又稱纖毛蟲。根據本草綱目記載，該蟲可壯陽，黑鬚髮，悅顏色，久服長筋骨，益精髓。根據北京大學科學院左2016年研究指出海毛蟲含豐富卵磷脂，可以防止男士脫髮，白發，因此亦在海中何首烏之稱。<br />\n<br />\n海毛蟲亦含豐富的磷酸二酯酶，或可治療男士性功能障礙並有壯陽之功效，此外海毛蟲亦含各種豐富的維生素礦物質，其蛋白質含量更是同等牛肉的20倍，而且肉質細嫩鮮美，在香港更有小瀨尿蝦（即蝦蛄）之稱，海毛蟲在中國境內並不常見，但近來，香港當地海上及沙灘突然湧出大量野生海毛蟲，因此亦造成香港人吃海毛蟲的熱潮，專家指出，近來由於是海毛蟲的繁殖季節，加上各地火山爆發，地震等激烈版塊運動令各地海毛蟲紛紛湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n海毛蟲的刺有毒，可導致皮膚敏感，所以捕捉時必須小心並戴上手套，食用亦須小心把毛除掉並去掉內臟方可食用，海毛蟲肉質鮮美，只須火烤灑上鹽便可放心食用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#邊個咁大整古<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35726455906948cc2225ae49a726b4685a5d4d6","tid":712363,"uid":23581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"屌 你地仲係咁講<br />\n我今朝去沙灘已經捉唔到啦<br />\n比大陸人見到又黎同我地爭"},{"pid":"20ec59b6d0da05160d92d371095ef6dc2757de5a","tid":712363,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"做多左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a759960d254374197244d05f619dfee4ab14888","tid":712363,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"好想食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a2e2e179ab4f9e56987c1384ecc51f96b10e79","tid":712363,"uid":157710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/710623/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/710623/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"580d3f96bbb68b535e41dbb42f69336bf725be3e","tid":712363,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"支那上到wiki咩"},{"pid":"a2308bcc1abf321a9d69f10cfb68a90a65a75e58","tid":712363,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母<br />\nwiki都玩<br />\n小學雞唔識分輕重<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"dd3e4ddf3b0dfa72e755d69ddedd2707152fa52a","tid":712363,"uid":109173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"Child登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4816d53db914de988a2f980da8bfb1d0d6ddb334","tid":712363,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"580d3f96bbb68b535e41dbb42f69336bf725be3e","tid":712363,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"支那上到wiki咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"WIKI 一早係大陸陣地喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}